channel.description:
Hi there Well I just released A server called "Rsc-Power" I will have the screen shots Shortly give me a few minutes please And also The server is incomplete! But still it's pretty fun right now And i guess i ALready have 11 members online so far So please come And join us. Just all I gotta do Is add a few more Stuff... The website is in my sig.
